These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: pepper, broccoli, mango, nectarine, carrot, cherry, zucchini
There are 7 different nationalities: chinese, malaysian, nigerian, japanese, argentine, polish, australian
 1. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating nectarine is not the polish##6
 3. the chinese is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
 4. the australian is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5
 5. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 6. the chinese is on the right of the person eating mango##1
 7. the person eating cherry is somewhere between the person eating broccoli and the malaysian##7
 8. the malaysian is on the left of the australian##1
 9. the japanese is somewhere between the person eating carrot and the nigerian##7
10. the nigerian is on the left or right of the chinese##3
11. the argentine is on the far left##1
12. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
13. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the right of the person eating cherry##5
14. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the right of the person eating carrot##5
15. the person eating carrot is the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | mango    | pepper    | broccoli | cherry | nectarine | carrot    | zucchini |
| Nationality   | argentine | chinese | nigerian  | polish   | japanese    | malaysian | australian |

