.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, cherry, kiwi, pepper, watermelon, pumpkin, peach
The people have 7 different hobbies: woodworking, drawing, dancing, sudoku, board-games, magic-tricks, filmmaking
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere between the person eating peach and the person eating cherry##7
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person eating pepper##1
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 5. the person eating apple is somewhere between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
 6. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere between the person eating pepper and the person who's hobby is dancing##7
 7. the person eating watermelon is somewhere between the person eating pepper and the person eating cherry##7
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 9. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person eating watermelon##5
10. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not the person eating peach##6
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
13. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person eating pepper##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | peach  | kiwi | pumpkin | pepper | apple     | watermelon | cherry  |
| Hobby   | dancing | magic-tricks | drawing  | filmmaking  | board-games | sudoku      | woodworking |

