 9. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the fan of salsa and the fan of dubstep##7
10. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the fan of reggae##6
13. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is card-games##7
14. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
15. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
16. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the fan of folk##6
